th=\"1200\" height=\"600\" title=\"The 2019 Guide to Buying Active Instagram Followers without Wasting Your Money\" alt=\"The 2019 Guide to Buying Active Instagram Followers without Wasting Your Money\" style=\"width: 100%!important;\"></a></p><p style=\"padding: 0 26px !important; margin: 0 !important;\">In most instances of brands or influencers buying Instagram followers, the rate of engagement does not go up even after thousands of followers have been purchased and there is no tangible difference to the impact your Instagram account creates on raising brand awareness, building a community or even driving traffic to the website for conversions. [&#8230;]<p style=\"margin: 0!important;padding: 26px 0 0!important;\"><a href=\"https://oceanwp.org/blog/the-2019-guide-to-buying-active-instagram-followers-without-wasting-your-money/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: inline-block; padding: 10px 30px; color: #ffffff; background-color: #13aff0; border-radius: 30px; font-size: 13px; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.4; text-transform: uppercase; text-align: center; text-decoration: none; letter-spacing: 1px;\">Read More</a></p></p>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:12:\"Walter Moore\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:8109:\"<p style=\"display: block; padding: 0 0 24px; margin: 0 !important;\"><a href=\"https://oceanwp.org/blog/the-2019-guide-to-buying-active-instagram-followers-without-wasting-your-money/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/instagram-cell-phone-tablet-device-163184-1.jpeg\" width=\"1200\" height=\"600\" title=\"The 2019 Guide to Buying Active Instagram Followers without Wasting Your Money\" alt=\"The 2019 Guide to Buying Active Instagram Followers without Wasting Your Money\" style=\"width: 100%!important;\"></a></p><p style=\"padding: 0 26px !important; margin: 0 !important;\">\n<p>In\nmost instances of brands or influencers buying Instagram followers, the rate of\nengagement does not go up even after thousands of followers have been purchased\nand there is no tangible difference to the impact your Instagram account\ncreates on raising brand awareness, building a community or even driving\ntraffic to the website for conversions. This is the main reason why professional\nInstagram marketers consider buying Instagram followers to be a complete waste of\nmoney and warn against being tempted by advertisements promising thousands of\nfollowers for just a few dollars. The main reason why the strategy of buying\nInstagram followers does not succeed in most cases is that typically only fake\naccounts operated by computerized bots were bought and not real and active\nInstagram followers.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Why Buying Fake Followers for Your\nInstagram Account Is Risky? </strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p>The\nmain reasons why brands or influencers look to increase their follower counts\non Instagram by buying followers are to improve their account statistics to increase\ntheir advertising earnings potential and to boost their social proof to\nencourage other Instagram users to follow them. However, buying poor-quality\nfake Instagram followers put the brands and influencers at risk in two main\nways:</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Fake followers reduce the potential of\ninfluencers to strike up partnerships with brands</strong>: Advertisers and brands looking at\ndeveloping relationships with influencers to leverage their followers to\nincrease brand reach have no use for influencers who have built up their follower\ncounts with inactive and bought-out followers. Brands just need to take a look\nat the follower-to-engagement ratio to figure out that the influencer has\nbought low-quality fake followers just to bump up the statistics; typically\neven with hundreds of thousands of followers, the engagement ratio is less than\n1%, which acts like a surefire alert to brands that the influencer does not\nseem to have any influence at all. </p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Accounts with fake followers punished\nby Instagram</strong>: The\nInstagram algorithm also very actively scans accounts for unusually low\nengagement rates but having large follower bases. The algorithm has evolved to\nthe extent that it automatically purges accounts of the likes generated by bots\nand pushes down the visibility of the posts in the feeds of followers, as\nreported by <a href=\"https://influencermarketinghub.com\">https://influencermarketinghub.com</a>. Buying fake bot-generated followers\nis just the same as flushing your money down the drain. Not only they do not\nachieve anything good for your brand but also it is almost impossible to\nrecover from the ruined engagement rate unless you embark upon a deliberate\naction of getting the fake followers unfollowed.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>How to Buy Instagram Followers and\nStill Benefit? </strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Instead\nof signing up with an agency that delivers only bot-generated followers and\nautomatic likes and comments that get your account penalized, the best way of\nbuilding your account potential is to buy Instagram followers that are active.\nTypically, the marketing agencies like <a href=\"https://blastup.com/\">blastup</a> offer\nbrands and influencers legitimate Instagram accounts that are operated by real\npeople who will take an active interest in the content you post giving you the\nmuch-wanted likes and comments without the feel that automated systems do.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>It\ncan take a lot of time and effort to conduct the research your target audience,\nengage with them meaningfully as well as establish enduring partnerships with\nother Instagram accounts for getting organic growth in the number of followers\nand engagement rate. Spending on Instagram advertising, while being effective,\ncan be quite expensive and not necessarily suited to all budgets. At an\nestimated $5 per thousand impressions assuming an engagement rate of 2%, it can\ncost $0.25 to acquire each follower. Realistically, the engagement rate is\nlikely to be far lower till you discover an advertising strategy that is really\neffective so you can assume that the cost per follower will be more likely\naround double that or $0.50, which means an expense of $500 or more to acquire\njust one thousand followers. However, a good workaround is buying active\nInstagram followers from marketing agencies.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Safely Buying Active Instagram\nFollowers</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p>The\nrisks of buying followers from bot-based services are clear; you end up not\nonly wasting your money but also spoiling your reputation making it difficult\nto monetize your account. However, there are numerous services that promise to\nmake available Instagram followers that are real which can be very attractive\nto boost the performance of your account. However, you need to be very careful\nthat you engage genuine service providers offering real Instagram followers and\nare not being scammed by bot services.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Buy targeted followers</strong>: The quality and demographics of your\nfollowers are of utmost importance. If the service provider does not ask for\nthe details of the target audience profiles, most effective hashtags, and who\nyour competitors are, you could be buying random bot-based followers instead of\nan engaged audience.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Beware of cheap services</strong>: Even though you can expect buying\nfollowers to be far less expensive than running Instagram ad campaigns, you\nshould be beware of services that are offering followers at prices that seem\nunrealistically cheap. You can be very sure that these followers are not going\nto be good quality active accounts that are likely to be purged by Instagram\nfor being bot accounts.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Engage sellers with transparent\nmethodologies</strong>: Since\nbuying followers have traditionally been viewed with suspicion, you should ask\nthe seller regarding how they will target followers. While you can‚Äôt expect\nthem to give you specifics, they should be in a position to explain their\nstrategy for increasing your engagement rate and give you a credible proof of\ntheir success with other accounts.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Focus on engagement growth</strong>: Even though the follower count is an\nimportant metric for attracting brand advertising and influencer opportunities,\nit is the engagement rate that is what you should really focus on for\nincreasing brand awareness and visibility. Insist on getting a performance\nguarantee from the service provider regarding engagement growth to prevent them\nfrom giving you bot-based followers.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Conclusion </strong>\n\nIt\nis important to not to be obsessed with the follower count of your Instagram\naccount even though it is perhaps the first metric that brands take note of.\nThe real value of your Instagram account is the extent of the engagement of\nyour followers, and to achieve a reasonably high engagement rate, you need to\nacquire real Instagram followers, not machine generated likes or comments.\n\n\n\n</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0!important;padding: 26px 0 0!important;\"><a href=\"https://oceanwp.org/blog/the-2019-guide-to-buying-active-instagram-followers-without-wasting-your-money/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: inline-block; padding: 10px 30px; color: #ffffff; background-color: #13aff0; border-radius: 30px; font-size: 13px; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.4; text-transform: uppercase; text-align: center; text-decoration: none; letter-spacing: 1px;\">Read More</a></p></p>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http