Guide To Embedding Videos In WordPress in 2019\" style=\"width: 100%!important;\"></a></p><p style=\"padding: 0 26px !important; margin: 0 !important;\">You‚Äôve read a lot of video storytelling tips, and can‚Äôt wait to add new videos to your website? This is exactly what this article helps you to do. Read on to learn how to embed any video on your WordPress website. How to embed any video If you don‚Äôt want to read the whole thing, [&#8230;]<p style=\"margin: 0!important;padding: 26px 0 0!important;\"><a href=\"https://oceanwp.org/blog/the-ultimate-guide-to-embedding-videos-in-wordpress-in-2019/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: inline-block; padding: 10px 30px; color: #ffffff; background-color: #13aff0; border-radius: 30px; font-size: 13px; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.4; text-transform: uppercase; text-align: center; text-decoration: none; letter-spacing: 1px;\">Read More</a></p></p>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"James Scott\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11930:\"<p style=\"display: block; padding: 0 0 24px; margin: 0 !important;\"><a href=\"https://oceanwp.org/blog/the-ultimate-guide-to-embedding-videos-in-wordpress-in-2019/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/rsz_device-laptop-people-1321732_3.jpg\" width=\"1200\" height=\"600\" title=\"The Ultimate Guide To Embedding Videos In WordPress in 2019\" alt=\"The Ultimate Guide To Embedding Videos In WordPress in 2019\" style=\"width: 100%!important;\"></a></p><p style=\"padding: 0 26px !important; margin: 0 !important;\">		<div data-elementor-type=\"post\" data-elementor-id=\"395430\" class=\"elementor elementor-395430\" data-elementor-settings=\"[]\">\n			<div class=\"elementor-inner\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-section-wrap\">\n							<section class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-7fd18308 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default elementor-section elementor-top-section\" data-id=\"7fd18308\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n						<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-6482f3fc elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column\" data-id=\"6482f3fc\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n			<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap  elementor-element-populated\">\n					<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2b4fbbe4 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"2b4fbbe4\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n					<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\">You‚Äôve read a lot of <a href=\"https://oceanwp.org/blog/13-tips-and-case-studies-on-using-video-storytelling-in-your-marketing-strategy/\">video storytelling tips</a>, and can‚Äôt wait to add new videos to your website? This is exactly what this article helps you to do.\n\nRead on to learn how to embed any video on your WordPress website.\n<h3>How to embed any video</h3>\nIf you don‚Äôt want to read the whole thing, here are two ways you can embed any video on your website.\n<h3>1 The shortcut</h3>\nSome websites do not require you to do any work on embedding them. You don‚Äôt have to head on to the website, click anything, and handle the settings. All that you have to do is just to copy the link to the video you want, and paste it to a WordPress page.\n\nThe thing is, some websites are whitelisted by WordPress. This allows the platform to embed videos from these websites automatically.\n\nIf you copy a link to one of the most popular services, you are probably going to see it auto-embedded on your website. These whitelisted websites include Amazon, Facebook, Instagram, Reddit, Twitter, and YouTube.\n\nWordPress has a dozen of other, less prominent, websites whitelisted as well.\n<h3>2 The code</h3>\nDo you know a bit of HTML? If you do, brush up on your skills as you are going to have to implement them.\n\nUsing code allows you to have the widest array of options possible. The basic code for embedding videos looks like this:\n\n<img class=\"wp-image-396363 size-full aligncenter\" src=\"https://oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/203aa6793a03f8eb3d7f0d6dad39006c.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"265\" height=\"56\" />\n\nHowever, you can add a lot of things to this base code. You can add things like the exact height and width to your embed, or block certain features of the video you don‚Äôt want to see on your page.\n\nSome of the features that were accessible before are obsolete since HTML5 came out. You can still use them with a CSS entry.\n<h3>How to embed YouTube videos in WordPress</h3>\nIf the first option was too basic and the second too hard for you, it‚Äôs time to follow the middle ground. Embedding videos from platforms via copying the embed code directly from there is best for most webmasters.\n\nThe thing is, you have a lot more options than an embed gives you, but it‚Äôs way easier than writing the code manually.\n\nPress the ‚ÄúShare‚Äù button while on YouTube, and go on to the ‚ÄúEmbed‚Äù option. Here‚Äôs what you will see.\n\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-396328 size-full\" src=\"https://oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Youtube_embed.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1284\" height=\"478\" srcset=\"//oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Youtube_embed.jpg 1284w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Youtube_embed-300x112.jpg 300w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Youtube_embed-768x286.jpg 768w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Youtube_embed-1024x381.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1284px) 100vw, 1284px\" />\n\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">From here, you have two major options ‚Äì giving the users controls, and starting the video at a certain time. The options that are listed in the ‚Äúallow‚Äù tag help your mobile users to rotate the video by rotating the device and using the picture-in-picture mode on Android.</span>\n<h3>How to embed Vimeo videos</h3>\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Vimeo has a reputation of hosting videos other websites are too afraid to host because they‚Äôre so edgy. It has some great cinematography on as well. If you need to embed a Vimeo video, here‚Äôs how you do it.</span>\n\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">However, is no different to YouTube when it comes to embedding videos. Press the ‚ÄúShare‚Äù and go down to see the ‚ÄúEmbed‚Äù option. Click on ‚ÄúShow options‚Äù to see what you can choose.</span>\n\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-396335 size-full\" src=\"https://oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Vimeo_embed.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"548\" height=\"654\" srcset=\"//oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Vimeo_embed.jpg 548w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Vimeo_embed-251x300.jpg 251w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 548px) 100vw, 548px\" />\n\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Vimeo has a whole lot of options you can choose from. You can make the size of the player responsive or fixed, make the video loop to make for a great background or choose a color.</span>\n<h3>How to embed TikTok Video</h3>\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">TikTok has gained a lot of attention recently. It started with some lip synch videos, and now people post all sorts of entertaining videos there. Here‚Äôs how you go about embedding one of the videos on your own website.</span>\n\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">All you have to do is to press the ‚ÄúGet Embed Code‚Äù button. The problem is, however, you don‚Äôt have any options to choose from.</span>\n\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">After copying the code, you get a link for 340&#215;700 player with autoplay. You can fix the settings on your WordPress page later.</span>\n\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-396336 size-full\" src=\"https://oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/TikTik_embed.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"641\" height=\"610\" srcset=\"//oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/TikTik_embed.jpg 641w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/TikTik_embed-300x285.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 641px) 100vw, 641px\" />\n<h3>How to embed Imgur videos</h3>\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Imgur is the unofficial source of fun and meme-worthy videos on the web. It‚Äôs also a great hosting option for videos.</span>\n\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Getting an embed link is very easy, just press the ‚ÄúEmbed Post‚Äù button.</span>\n\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-396337 size-full\" src=\"https://oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/367496f0f52ea9daedf72d32e97242a6.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"598\" height=\"568\" srcset=\"//oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/367496f0f52ea9daedf72d32e97242a6.png 598w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/367496f0f52ea9daedf72d32e97242a6-300x285.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 598px) 100vw, 598px\" />\n\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">However, your embed is going to have a peculiar look. The thing is, Imgur wants to create a similar style across the web and let people share their videos. This is why they make embeds look like this.</span>\n\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-396339 size-full\" src=\"https://oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/cfe83a16b1aca269c1b9b8900ab3a2bb.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"429\" height=\"553\" srcset=\"//oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/cfe83a16b1aca269c1b9b8900ab3a2bb.png 429w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/cfe83a16b1aca269c1b9b8900ab3a2bb-233x300.png 233w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 429px) 100vw, 429px\" />\n<h3>How to embed your own video</h3>\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Do you have your own video you want to embed? It‚Äôs better to upload it to third-party website and stream it to your WordPress site. It makes your website faster since it doesn‚Äôt have to deal with tens or hundreds of megabytes of data that is your video.</span>\n\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Here‚Äôs how you do it.</span>\n<h3><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">1 Edit &amp; Convert</span></h3>\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Some video formats are weird and won‚Äôt be accepted at some hostings. Some just weigh too much. What you can do is convert the video to either .mp4 or .webm. These two formats are accepted universally.</span>\n\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Look at what this </span><a href=\"https://www.movavi.com/videoeditor/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">video editor</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> allows you to pick in terms of formats.</span>\n\n<a href=\"https://www.movavi.com/\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-396341 size-full\" src=\"https://oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Movavi_embed.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1900\" height=\"1000\" srcset=\"//oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Movavi_embed.jpg 1900w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Movavi_embed-300x158.jpg 300w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Movavi_embed-768x404.jpg 768w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Movavi_embed-1024x539.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1900px) 100vw, 1900px\" /></a>\n\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">You will also be able to edit your video in Movavi video editor, so you‚Äôll save yourself some time by using one software instead of many. </span>\n<h3><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">2 Upload your video</span></h3>\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Once you‚Äôre done with Movavi, you have to upload your video. Choose a reliable platform that offers a lot of variability with embeds. Go for Vimeo or YouTube as they‚Äôre the fastest ones.</span>\n\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">You can also try to upload the video to one of the many .webm hostings if you want, but that has no advantages in embedded videos. You can try doing that for background videos, though.</span>\n<h3>How to embed video with a plugin</h3>\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">If you checked out our article about </span><a href=\"https://oceanwp.org/blog/7-top-plugins-to-turn-a-wordpress-site-into-a-mobile-app/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">plugins that turn your website into an app</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">, you know that there are a lot of plugins to use when it comes to WordPress.</span>\n\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">You can use a multitude of those for embedding videos. Try Easy Video Player for making embeds. It‚Äôs free to use and widens your options with how the videos are displayed to the maximum.</span>\n\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">If you‚Äôre not keen on having many options and just want to auto-embed videos from all over the web, try Advanced Responsive Video Embedder. It‚Äôs free as well.</span></div>\n				</div>\n				</div>\n						</div>\n			</div>\n		</div>\n						</div>\n			</div>\n		</section>\n						</div>\n			</div>\n		</div>\n		<p style=\"margin: 0!important;padding: 26px 0 0!important;\"><a href=\"https://oceanwp.org/blog/the-ultimate-guide-to-embedding-videos-in-wordpress-in-2019/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: inline-block; padding: 10px 30px; color: #ffffff; background-color: #13aff0; border-radius: 30px; font-size: 13px; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.4; text-transform: uppercase; text-align: center; text-decoration: none; letter-spacing: 1px;\">Read More</a></p></p>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:90:\"https://oceanwp.org/blog/the-ultimate-guide-to-embedding-videos-in-wordpress-in-2019/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"